'''''Oceana''''' was a [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class T-4a shuttle]] of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] that carried [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] [[Kupalo]] on his transfer from [[Defiance/Legends|''Defiance'']] to the [[Liberty/Legends|''Liberty'']]. The [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttle]] was escorted by two [[Delta-class DX-9 stormtrooper transport|''Delta''-class DX-9 stormtrooper transports]], [[Azure (transport group)|''Azure'']].

